wdi2-SH.DYN.1519.def: Probability of dying between age 15-19 years of age expressed per 1,000 adolescents age 15, if subject to age-specific mortality rates of the specified year.
wdi2-SH.DYN.1519.name: Probability of dying among adolescents ages 15-19 years
wdi2-SH.DYN.1519.source: Estimates developed by the UN Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation (UNICEF, WHO, World Bank, UN DESA Population Division) at www.childmortality.org.
